Proposals**: Photochemical and surface-driven processes.\n\n---\n\n### Conclusion\nThe prebiotic synthesis of valine likely involved a combination of pathways, including the Strecker reaction, hydrothermal processes, and cyanide/formaldehyde chemistry. While experimental evidence supports these mechanisms, significant gaps remain in understanding the environmental constraints, reaction yields, and the transition to biotic pathways. Future research should focus on addressing these challenges to provide a more comprehensive picture of valine's role in the origins of life.\n=== END KNOWLEDGE BASE RESEARCH FINDINGS ===\n\n=== END LITERATURE RESEARCH ===\n\nConsider how well the network aligns with this literature in your evaluation.\n\n\nPlease evaluate the network and respond with JSON:\n{\n    \"pathway_evaluations\": [\n        {\n            \"pathway_id\": \"<id>\",\n            \"reaction_scores\": {\"rxn_001\": 0.85, ...},\n            \"chemical_feasibility\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"pathway_coherence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"environmental_progression\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"target_achievement\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"overall_confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n            \"feedback\": \"<pathway-specific feedback>\",\n            \"approved\": <true if confidence >= 0.8>,\n            \"problematic_reactions\": [\"rxn_ids with issues\"],\n            \"suggestions\": [\"improvements\"]\n        }\n    ],\n    \"best_pathway_id\": \"<id of best pathway>\",\n    \"overall_confidence\": <0.0-1.0>,\n    \"network_feedback\": \"<overall assessment>\",\n    \"approved\": <true if any pathway approved>,\n    \"hub_quality\": <0.0-1.0>,\n    \"convergence_quality\": <0.0-1.0>\n}\n", "raw_response": "", "parsed_response": null, "reasoning": "", "duration_ms": 10982.13815689087, "success": false, "error_message": "{'type': 'error', 'error': {'details': None, 'type': 'api_error', 'message': 'Internal server error'}, 'request_id': 'req_011CZ8HTJpyGm78xGHf1UtC6'}"}
